latestIgtvVideos.title: Beauty Box by @myskinq - Active Facials at Home.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Anybody who knows me, can tell you how much I stress on keeping your skin clean. 

I love trying out home remedies. And this week, thanks to @myskinq I got to try this very detailed, yet oh so simple beauty box, consisting of these basic five step ‘at home’ facial. Along with an additional elixir and sun protect gel.

The products are Paraben-free, sulphate-free, silicon free, phthalates free & GMO free. 

Favorite pick from the lot- The Massage butter & sun protect gel! ❤️
